{
  "title": "挂载",
  "cells": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "data": "<h1>Ubuntu篇</h1><div><a href=\"https://help.ubuntu.com/community/Fstab\">https://help.ubuntu.com/community/Fstab</a><br></div><div>配置文件<span style=\"font-family: monospace; line-height: 13px; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">/etc/fstab</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.4;\">中记载了自动进行<font color=\"#323232\" style=\"background-color: rgb(254, 250, 0);\">分区挂载</font>的必要信息。简单地说，挂载是裸分区准备接收访问以及获取文件系统中对应位置的过程。</span></div><div><ol><li>一般情况下fstab用户固定设备的挂载，比如CD/DVD设备，网络共享设备。可移动设备比如闪存驱动器，可以放到fstab中，但是它们一般会通过<span style=\"font-family: Ubuntu, 'Ubuntu Beta', 'Bitstream Vera Sans', 'DejaVu Sans', Tahoma, sans-serif; line-height: 19.5px; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">gnome-volume-manager进行挂载，因此本文不探讨这一过程。</span></li><li><span style=\"font-family: Ubuntu, 'Ubuntu Beta', 'Bitstream Vera Sans', 'DejaVu Sans', Tahoma, sans-serif; line-height: 19.5px; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">mout和fstab的选项是类似的。</span></li><li><span style=\"font-family: Ubuntu, 'Ubuntu Beta', 'Bitstream Vera Sans', 'DejaVu Sans', Tahoma, sans-serif; line-height: 19.5px; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">fstab文件中列出的分区可以设置成启动时挂载。<br></span></li><li><span style=\"font-family: Ubuntu, 'Ubuntu Beta', 'Bitstream Vera Sans', 'DejaVu Sans', Tahoma, sans-serif; line-height: 19.5px; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">没有写入到fstab中的设备必须要通过root用户进行挂载。</span></li></ol><div style=\"widows: 1;\"><font face=\"Ubuntu, Ubuntu Beta, Bitstream Vera Sans, DejaVu Sans, Tahoma, sans-serif\"><span style=\"line-height: 19.5px;\"><br></span></font></div></div><div style=\"widows: 1;\"><font face=\"Ubuntu, Ubuntu Beta, Bitstream Vera Sans, DejaVu Sans, Tahoma, sans-serif\"><span style=\"line-height: 19.5px;\">该文件的语法是这样的：</span></font></div><div style=\"widows: 1;\"><pre style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 4pt; border: 1px dashed rgb(193, 180, 150); line-height: 16px; font-family: UbuntuMono, courier, monospace; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; word-wrap: break-word; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);\">[<span style=\"font-family: Ubuntu, 'Ubuntu Beta', 'Bitstream Vera Sans', 'DejaVu Sans', Tahoma, sans-serif; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\">设备</span>] [<span style=\"font-family: Ubuntu, 'Ubuntu Beta', 'Bitstream Vera Sans', 'DejaVu Sans', Tahoma, sans-serif; line-height: 19px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">挂载点</span>] [文件系统] [Options] [Dump] [Pass]</pre></div><div style=\"widows: 1;\"><font face=\"Ubuntu, Ubuntu Beta, Bitstream Vera Sans, DejaVu Sans, Tahoma, sans-serif\"><span style=\"line-height: 19.5px;\"><br></span></font></div><div style=\"widows: 1;\"><table style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 13px; font-family: Ubuntu, 'Ubuntu Beta', 'Bitstream Vera Sans', 'DejaVu Sans', Tahoma, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><tbody style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; line-height: 1; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><tr style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; line-height: 1; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><td style=\"margin: 1px; padding: 4px; border-color: rgb(233, 233, 233); font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; text-align: center; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(254, 183, 109);\"><p class=\"line891\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 8px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; text-align: left; vertical-align: baseline;\"><b>字段</b></p></td><td style=\"margin: 1px; padding: 4px; border-color: rgb(233, 233, 233); font-style: inherit; line-height: 1; font-family: inherit; text-align: center; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(254, 183, 109);\"><p class=\"line891\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 8px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-family: inherit; text-align: left; vertical-align: baseline;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; line-height: 1; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">解释</strong></p></td></tr><tr style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; line-height: 1; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><td style=\"margin: 1px; padding: 4px; border-color: rgb(233, 233, 233); font-style: inherit; line-height: 1; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span class=\"anchor\" id=\"line-25\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; line-height: 1; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span><p class=\"line862\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 8px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">&lt;设备&gt;</p></td><td style=\"margin: 1px; padding: 4px; border-color: rgb(233, 233, 233); font-style: inherit; line-height: 1; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><p class=\"line862\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 8px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: 1.5;\">包含文件系统的设备或分区（用/dev内的位置或者UUID来表示）</span><br></p><p class=\"line862\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 8px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: 1.5;\">Ubuntu现在使用UUID来区分各个分区。列出各个分区的UUID可以使用<code>blkid</code>命令。</span></p><pre style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 4pt; border: 1px dashed rgb(193, 180, 150); line-height: 16px; font-family: UbuntuMono, courier, monospace; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; word-wrap: break-word; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);\">sudo blkid</pre><p class=\"line862\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 8px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">其他的引用方式：</p><p class=\"line862\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 8px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">设备：&nbsp;<span style=\"line-height: 19.5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit;\">/dev/sdxy</span></p><p class=\"line862\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 8px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"line-height: 19.5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Label : LABEL=lable</span><span style=\"font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: 1.5;\"><br></span></p><p class=\"line862\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 8px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"line-height: 19.5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">网络：</span></p><p class=\"line862\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 8px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></p><ul><li><span style=\"line-height: 19.5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit;\">Samba&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height: 19.5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">: //server/share</span><br></li><li><span style=\"line-height: 19.5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">N</span><span style=\"line-height: 19.5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">FS : server:/share</span></li><li><span style=\"line-height: 19.5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">S</span><span style=\"line-height: 19.5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">SHFS : sshfs#user@server:/share</span></li></ul><p></p><p class=\"line862\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 8px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: 1.5;\"><br></span></p></td></tr><tr style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; line-height: 1; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><td style=\"margin: 1px; padding: 4px; border-color: rgb(233, 233, 233); font-style: inherit; line-height: 1; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span class=\"anchor\" id=\"line-26\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; line-height: 1; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span><p class=\"line862\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 8px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">&lt;挂载点&gt;</p></td><td style=\"margin: 1px; padding: 4px; border-color: rgb(233, 233, 233); font-style: inherit; line-height: 1; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><p class=\"line862\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 8px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: 1.5;\">文件系统中对应的目录，你可以通过该目录访问该设备或者分区内的内容（注意，</span><font color=\"#323232\" style=\"font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(254, 250, 0);\">交换空间没有挂载点</font><span style=\"font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: 1.5;\">）。</span></p><p class=\"line862\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 8px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></p><ul><li><span style=\"font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: 1.5;\">挂载点不要有空格！</span><br></li><li><span style=\"font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: 1.5;\">挂载之前挂载点要先行创建。</span></li></ul><p></p></td></tr><tr style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; line-height: 1; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><td style=\"margin: 1px; padding: 4px; border-color: rgb(233, 233, 233); font-style: inherit; line-height: 1; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span class=\"anchor\" id=\"line-27\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; line-height: 1; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span><p class=\"line862\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 8px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">&lt;文件系统<span style=\"font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit;\">类型</span><span style=\"font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit;\">&gt;</span><span style=\"font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: 1.5;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p></td><td style=\"margin: 1px; padding: 4px; border-color: rgb(233, 233, 233); font-style: inherit; line-height: 1; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><p class=\"line862\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 8px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">文件系统的类型 (see&nbsp;<a href=\"https://help.ubuntu.com/community/LinuxFilesystemsExplained\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; line-height: 1; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(221, 72, 20); text-decoration: none;\">LinuxFilesystemsExplained</a>).</p><p class=\"line862\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 8px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">可以使用auto或者特定的文件系统类型。使用auto时系统会自动检测目标的文件系统，大部分情况下都能正确诊断。</p><p class=\"line862\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 8px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">可用的值有：</p><p class=\"line862\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 8px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><ul><li><span style=\"font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: 1.5;\">auto</span><br></li><li><span style=\"font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: 1.5;\">vfat - FAT分区</span></li><li><span style=\"font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: 1.5;\">ntfs - NTFS分区</span></li><li>ext4, ext3, ext2, jfs, 等等</li><li>udf, iso9660 - CD/DVD</li><li>swap</li></ul></p></td></tr><tr style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; line-height: 1; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><td style=\"margin: 1px; padding: 4px; border-color: rgb(233, 233, 233); font-style: inherit; line-height: 1; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span class=\"anchor\" id=\"line-28\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; line-height: 1; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span><p class=\"line862\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 8px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">&lt;options&gt;</p></td><td style=\"margin: 1px; padding: 4px; border-color: rgb(233, 233, 233); font-style: inherit; line-height: 1; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><p class=\"line862\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 8px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">挂载选项 (see the man page for&nbsp;<tt style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; line-height: 1; vertical-align: baseline;\">mount</tt>).</p><p class=\"line862\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 8px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><br></p></td></tr><tr style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; line-height: 1; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><td style=\"margin: 1px; padding: 4px; border-color: rgb(233, 233, 233); font-style: inherit; line-height: 1; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span class=\"anchor\" id=\"line-29\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; line-height: 1; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span><p class=\"line862\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 8px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">&lt;dump&gt;</p></td><td style=\"margin: 1px; padding: 4px; border-color: rgb(233, 233, 233); font-style: inherit; line-height: 1; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><p class=\"line862\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 8px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">开启或者禁用设备的备份 (the command&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; line-height: 1; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">dump</span>). 设置为0表示禁用。1表示启用。一般设为0。</p></td></tr><tr style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; line-height: 1; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><td style=\"margin: 1px; padding: 4px; border-color: rgb(233, 233, 233); font-style: inherit; line-height: 1; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span class=\"anchor\" id=\"line-30\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; line-height: 1; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span><p class=\"line862\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 8px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">&lt;pass num&gt;</p></td><td style=\"margin: 1px; padding: 4px; border-color: rgb(233, 233, 233); font-style: inherit; line-height: 1; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><p class=\"line862\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 8px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: 1.5;\">控制</span><span style=\"line-height: 19.5px;\"><code>fsck</code>进行</span><span style=\"font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: 1.5;\">设备检错的顺序。根设备必须为1，其他设备应该为2， 设置为0表示禁用检测。</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div style=\"widows: 1;\"><font face=\"Ubuntu, Ubuntu Beta, Bitstream Vera Sans, DejaVu Sans, Tahoma, sans-serif\"><span style=\"line-height: 19.5px;\"><br></span></font></div><div style=\"widows: 1;\"><font face=\"Ubuntu, Ubuntu Beta, Bitstream Vera Sans, DejaVu Sans, Tahoma, sans-serif\"><span style=\"line-height: 19.5px;\">编辑fstab文件可以是用</span></font></div><div style=\"widows: 1;\"><font face=\"Ubuntu, Ubuntu Beta, Bitstream Vera Sans, DejaVu Sans, Tahoma, sans-serif\"><span style=\"line-height: 19.5px;\"><br></span></font></div><div style=\"widows: 1;\"><font face=\"Ubuntu, Ubuntu Beta, Bitstream Vera Sans, DejaVu Sans, Tahoma, sans-serif\"><span style=\"line-height: 19.5px;\"><br></span></font></div>"
    }
  ]
}